  "text": "A home page and unique logo were created for the Web site. The home page includes an introduction, instructions, and credits (Fig. 1) . To meet the needs of the student and to better understand the user demographics, we created a registration form. Each module includes pretest, list of learning objectives, review article, posttest, feedback, evaluation form, and certificate of completion (Figs. 2 and 3 ). This template was also used to create learning modules focused on the other five ACGME general competencies [CITATION_1] , including a module addressing professionalism and patient care issues titled \"How to Talk to the Pediatric Patient.\"",
